query:
insert into nft_direct_buy(
                address,
                root,
                nft,
                collection,
                price_token, 
                price, 
                buyer,
                finished_at,
                expired_at,
                state,
                created,
                updated,
                tx_lt
            )
            select
                unnest($1::varchar[]),
                unnest($2::varchar[]),
                unnest($3::varchar[]), 
                unnest($4::varchar[]),
                unnest($5::varchar[]), 
                unnest($6::numeric[]),
                unnest($7::varchar[]),
                unnest($8::timestamp[]),
                unnest($9::timestamp[]),
                unnest($10::direct_buy_state[]),
                unnest($11::timestamp[]),
                unnest($12::timestamp[]),
                unnest($13::bigint[])
            on conflict(address) do nothing
